records.name: Sheraton Maldives Full Moon Resort & Spa

location.address: Furanafushi Island, North Male’ Atoll, Republic Of Maldives

descriptions.direction: Located in Furanafushi Island, Sheraton Maldives Full Moon Resort & Spa is near the airport and on a private beach. Full Moon Beach is another place to visit that comes recommended. With windsurfing, fishing, and swimming nearby, you'll find plenty of adventures in the water.
descriptions.general: Set on a private island, just a 15 minute boat ride away from the Malé International Airport. The Sheraton Maldives Full Moon Resort and Spa welcomes guests into a world of golden sunshine, fine dining, water sports and entertainment, topped off with warm Maldivian hospitality. Situated by the beach in Furanafushi island in the North Male Atoll Maldives, 7.5 km from Malé International Airport by boat and 10 km from Male Main Island by boat. Price shown does NOT include arrival and return transfer, but is compulsory to book online Sunhotels POS,together with the hotel reservation. You are required to book the appropriate transfer and supply all the required transfer information. Hotel booking is not regarded as confirmed until the transfer booking has been completed. Facilities and services include restaurant, bar, lounge, gym, tennis court, swimming pool, children's pool, snack bar, kids club, wireless Internet access, laundry services (extra charge) and 24-hour reception. Rooms feature air conditioning, TV, safe, bathroom, minibar (extra charge), wireless Internet access, tea and coffee maker and telephone. Water bungalows and Water Villa is over the lagoon and also feature balcony/terrace. Cottage with Pool feature private pool, slippers, desk, day bed and closet. Please note that some of the above facilities may be closed due to weather / seasonal conditions. Please note that this is a villa complex (not private villas) with some facilities/services shared with other villas in the area. Due to the design of our Water Bungalow, Water Bungalow with Pool, Water villa and Water Suite cannot accommodate guests younger than 8 years and for children between 8-12 years, a waiver must be signed by legal guardian. Address: Furanafushi Island, North Male Atoll, Maldives, 08240
